name: James Timwo
description: I am an honest man looking for an honest woman to spend the rest of my life with, I am a man of integrity and I seek to love and be loved because that is the only thing on my mind. I want to feel the warmth of a woman’s heart. I love football though I can’t play but I am a very big fan of football, I like to go to the beach and I have dreams to live in the seaside with my lover and to listen to the beautiful sea sound and watch the wave at all time and also to enjoy nature to the fullest.
